				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Soloing in OOW New solo locations share them.<a name="63211"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 20 04 4:57 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Not many options that I've seen so far.  Many mobs summon, cast snare, dots or dds.
<br />

<br />
The most reliable soloing I've tried has been in Bloodfields swarm kiting the Dragorn rooms.  The little ones are charmable.  I swarm kited those down and and then chanted down any big ones left.
<br />

<br />
The problem is that they respawned as casters occasionally.  The large orange ones would sometimes spawn with the ability to cast a snare dot, and the little green ones would spawn back casting DDs on occasion.  Exp stunk at 66.
<br />

<br />
Also found 1 room in ruined city of dranik with 2 dragorns that I chant kited (lvl 66 mobs).  They also respawned casting schtuff.
<br />

<br />
Dragorns from what I have seen can't see invis, so if you have fade it is easy to play around....just circle a bit to see if they cast before laying on the dots.</span></td>
